Skills.Name: Cursed Edge

Skills.ShortDescription: Grants "Demon Power" on self. Inflicts 4-hit DMG on single enemy

Skills.Name: Sword Dance
Skills.Description: Raises ATK of all allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Further shields DMG ({1}% of skill user's ATK) by 15s if Human.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises ATK of all allies. Shields DMG if Human
